        <div class="msgSubject">UI redesign suggestions</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-16 00:17:23 | Edited: Nov 16 2010  2:44am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128988824370547803" id="quote-128988824370547803" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128988824370547803" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=173&amp;mid=128988824370547803&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128988824370547803&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128988824370547803" onclick="followToggle('add','128988824370547803')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
